items.headline: Welcome to the WikiStates Wikia!
items.desc: This Wikia is all about NationStates, the free online game created by Max Barry. You can create pages about your nation here. NationStates is a nation simulation game. Create a nation according to your political ideals and care for its people. Or deliberately oppress them. It's up to you. Users are welcome to contribute.
